name: Netbeans-TypoScript
body:
This Project aims to provide support for the TypoScript Language used by TYPO3. 

So far there is the lexer implemented, the TSScanner Class was developed on base of the t3editor tokenizetyposcript.js.

Furthermore, a very simple code completion has been implemented.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
